## Color palette for the game
## Based on warm/earthy tones with accent colors
class_name Palette
extends Object

## Light peachy - Use for: Highlights, text on dark backgrounds
const LIGHT_PEACH := Color("#f4ddd1")

## Light green - Use for: Success states, positive feedback, health
const LIGHT_GREEN := Color("#9cd762")

## Tan/Beige - Use for: Secondary UI elements, backgrounds
const TAN := Color("#e8b37b")

## Orange - Use for: Call-to-action buttons, important UI elements
const ORANGE := Color("#d2632c")

## Red-Orange - Use for: Warnings, important actions
const RED_ORANGE := Color("#a32c0f")

## Dark red - Use for: Danger, critical states
const DARK_RED := Color("#5e0000")

## Dark purple-red - Use for: Backgrounds, depth
const DARK_PURPLE_RED := Color("#78243e")

## Very dark purple - Use for: Deep backgrounds, borders
const VERY_DARK_PURPLE := Color("#24061d")
